Bug 978833 patch 9 - Add missing #includes in preparation for nsRuleWalker.h #include change in following patch.

Patch 10 changes nsRuleWalker.h from including StyleRule.h to including
Declaration.h; this fixes other headers to deal with that change based
on the include-what-you-use principle.

